# Dependency Management

- Scan for unused dependencies (`npm prune && npm ls --depth=0`).  
- Pin versions for production dependencies (avoid `^` or `latest`).  
- Group devDependencies separately.  
- After adding/removing a package, run a full build to catch missing modules.
